{"word":"χρή","slug":"χρή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>χρή</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ IE\">IE</a>] actually an old <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fem.\">fem.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ indecl.\">indecl.</a> noun meaning ‘that which should be/happen’, necessity, with the verb form <el>ἐστί</el> understood: <b>it is necessary <a href='B:660 3:10'>Js 3:10</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:χρεοφειλέτης/χρεωφειλέτης\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:χρῄζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}